## 2. Table Classes

Used across all data tables (campaigns, keywords, ad groups, targets, etc.).

| Class | Purpose | Key Styles |
|-------|---------|------------|
| `.table-container` | Outer wrapper | `sandstorm-s0` bg, 1px border, 12px radius, overflow hidden |
| `.table-header` | `<th>` elements | Left-aligned, 10px padding, 13.3px font, 500 weight, `#FEFEFB` bg, sortable cursor |
| `.table-cell` | `<td>` elements | 10px padding |
| `.table-header-cell` | Alternative header cell | 10px padding |
| `.table-row` | `<tr>` data rows | Bottom border, hover `#f3f4f6` |
| `.table-summary-row` | Total/summary rows | `#f5f5f0` bg, 600 weight |
| `.table-sticky-first-column` | First sticky column after checkbox | sticky left:35px, z:120, 13.3px font |
| `.table-text` | Standard cell text | 13.3px, `#0b0f16` color |
| `.table-edit-link` | Clickable text in table cells | 13.3px, truncated, hover: teal + underline |
| `.table-edit-icon` | Edit icon (appears on row hover) | Hidden by default, shows on `.group:hover` |

### Table Usage

```tsx
<div className="table-container">
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th className="table-header">Name</th>
        <th className="table-header">Status</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr className="table-row group">
        <td className="table-cell">
          <span className="table-edit-link">Campaign Name</span>
        </td>
        <td className="table-cell">
          <span className="table-text">Active</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
```

