## 4. Form Classes

| Class | Purpose | Key Styles |
|-------|---------|------------|
| `.form-label` | Form labels | 13px, 600 weight, `#072929`, 8px margin-bottom |
| `.form-label-small` | Small uppercase labels | 11.2px, 600 weight, `#556179`, uppercase |
| `.campaign-input` | Campaign form inputs | `#FEFEFB` bg, 40px height, 8px radius, 12px font, focus: green ring |
